on't look at me" while you dance...$k$pthe people watching will leave.$k\n$Wsラズワルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|...Ngh!!$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|I'm sorry for hurting your feelings.\nBut the battlefield is your stage, isn't it?$k$pIf someone's watching,\nyou don't get embarassed.$k$pBut why don't you take that\nto the actual stage?$k$p$E通常,|I too, have to have self-confidence\nwhile singing.$k\n$Wsラズワルド|$WaSelf-confidence...$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$Eキメ,|That's all I wanted to say. So then...\ngood luck with practice.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wd$w0|$Wsラズワルド|$Wa$E通常2,汗|Lady Aqua...$k$p...$k$p$E苦,汗|I...$k
