er also danced a dance like that\nto give people power on the battlefield.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa...$k$p$Eキメ,汗|But...my power can't be used\nwithout this pendant.$k$pSo it's not a good goal for you.$k\n$Wsラズワルド|$Wa$Eあらら,|Is that so...$k$p$E笑,|But, even if that pendant was gone,\nand that power was gone...$k$pThe fact that Lady Aqua's song\nis beautiful won't change.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑,|...Thank you.$k$pYou'll certainly become a wonderful dancer.$k$pSomeone who can cheer people up,\nand make them smile...$k$pYou'll have that kind of power.$k\n$Wsラズワルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes... I'm not there yet, but I'll\nbecome like that one day.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑2,|Then today, I'll sing for you as a\ncelebration of your first step.$k$p$E笑,|Will you...dance to my song,\nMr. Wonderful Dancer?$k\n$Wsラズワルド|$Wa$E笑,|Gladly, Miss Beautiful Songstress.$k
